Class ChangeAttributeOperation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.core.commands.operations.AbstractOperation

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IUndoableOperation, ITransactionalOperation

    public class ChangeAttributeOperation
extends AbstractOperation
implements ITransactionalOperation
    The ChangeAttributeOperation can be used to manipulate the value of an attribute of an IAttributeStore.
